fields.description: Time spent on meetings outside of working hours, which is based on the user's Outlook calendar setting for work hours. The value is represented in ISO 8601 format for durations.
fields.name: AfterHours

fields.description: Time spent in conflicting meetings (meetings that overlap with other meetings that the person accepted and where the personâ€™s status is set to Busy). The value is represented in ISO 8601 format for durations.

fields.description: Time spent in long meetings (more than an hour in duration). The value is represented in ISO 8601 format for durations.
fields.name: Long

fields.description: Time spent in meetings where the person was multitasking (read/sent more than a minimum number of emails and/or sent more than a minimum number of messages in Teams or in Skype for Business). The value is represented in ISO 8601 format for durations.
fields.name: Multitasking

fields.description: Time spent in meetings organized by the user. The value is represented in ISO 8601 format for durations.
fields.name: Organized

fields.name: Recurring
